@ThereIsAlwaysaWay2 In the comics, RS is portrayed in many ways depending on the artist, from a big and buff warrior, to a skinny waif. RS in this movie lost numerous fights, with at least 2 severe losses, and IIRC had a few scars but not too many since this is just the beginning of her time as the RS of legend, which begins with her god-gifted rebirth near the end of the movie.

Also, RS in the original comics doesn't suffer from "female weakness", as you put it, since she's granted strength and peerless fighting skill by a goddess. She's basically a Hyborian Age supersoldier. Captain Hyboria. 

It seems you never actually read any of the comics and are just faking it and ranting here because maybe you're an emasculated betamale angry at all the women who spurned you.

